statements: SELECT * FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE experiment_id = 1;
SELECT experiment_name, model_name, accuracy FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE model_name = 'ResNet';
SELECT dataset_name, model_name FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT * FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE end_time < '2022-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT model_name FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata;
SELECT experiment_name, model_name, dataset_name, accuracy FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY end_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE model_name LIKE 'C%' AND accuracy < 0.8 ORDER BY start_time ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE start_time BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY experiment_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT experiment_name, model_name, dataset_name, accuracy FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata ORDER BY experiment_name ASC, model_name DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT experiment_name, model_name, accuracy FROM deep_learning_experiments_metadata WHERE dataset_name = 'CIFAR-10' AND (accuracy < 0.7 OR accuracy > 0.85) ORDER BY accuracy DESC, experiment_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM experiment_metadata WHERE id = 1;
SELECT experiment_name, start_time FROM experiment_metadata ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiment_results WHERE result_accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT experiment_id, result_details FROM experiment_results WHERE result_id = 2;
SELECT id, experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM experiment_metadata;
SELECT * FROM experiment_metadata WHERE start_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT experiment_name, start_time FROM experiment_metadata ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, result_accuracy FROM experiment_results WHERE result_accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY result_accuracy DESC;
SELECT experiment_name, start_time, end_time FROM experiment_metadata WHERE experiment_name LIKE '%AI%';
SELECT result_id, result_details FROM experiment_results WHERE experiment_id = 3;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_owner FROM experiment_metadata;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_start_date, experiment_end_date FROM experiment_metadata;
SELECT model_name, model_type, model_accuracy FROM model_results;
SELECT model_id, model_loss, model_parameters FROM model_results;
SELECT experiment_id, model_id, learning_rate, batch_size, optimizer, epochs FROM hyperparameters;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_owner, experiment_start_date FROM experiment_metadata;
SELECT model_name, model_type, model_accuracy FROM model_results ORDER BY model_accuracy DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, model_id, learning_rate, optimizer FROM hyperparameters WHERE learning_rate < 0.01 AND optimizer = 'Adam';
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_end_date FROM experiment_metadata WHERE experiment_end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT model_name, model_accuracy, model_loss FROM model_results WHERE model_accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY model_accuracy DESC, model_loss ASC;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, start_date FROM experiments WHERE status = 'In Progress';
SELECT model_name, description, created_date FROM models ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_size FROM datasets WHERE upload_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT experiment_name, status, end_date FROM experiments WHERE status <> 'Completed';
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, start_date, status FROM experiments WHERE status='In Progress';
SELECT model_name, description FROM models WHERE model_name LIKE '%neural%';
SELECT AVG(accuracy) AS avg_accuracy, AVG(loss) AS avg_loss FROM results;

SELECT experiment_name, model_name, accuracy, evaluation_date FROM experiments e INNER JOIN results r ON e.experiment_id = r.experiment_id INNER JOIN models m ON r.model_id = m.model_id WHERE accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY evaluation_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, start_date, end_date FROM experiments WHERE status = 'completed';
SELECT model_name, model_type FROM models WHERE framework IS NOT NULL;
SELECT dataset_name, size_in_gb, created_date FROM datasets ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, model_id, dataset_id, execution_time FROM experiments_results WHERE loss < 0.05;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, start_date, status FROM experiments WHERE status = 'running';
SELECT model_name, model_type, framework FROM models ORDER BY model_name ASC;
SELECT dataset_name, size_in_gb FROM datasets WHERE size_in_gb > 10 ORDER BY size_in_gb DESC;

SELECT e.experiment_name, m.model_name, d.dataset_name, er.execution_time FROM experiments e JOIN experiments_results er ON e.experiment_id = er.experiment_id JOIN models m ON er.model_id = m.model_id JOIN datasets d ON er.dataset_id = d.dataset_id;
